author: lryan
msg: - Add support for oauth_body_hash signing as per http://oauth.googlecode.com/svn/spec/ext/body_hash/1.0/drafts/1/spec.html
- Add support for legacy body signing mechanism for backward compatability with old REST/RPC clients. Deprecated.
This change is a precusor to requiring strict content type checks for inbound REST/RPC requests
